哈喽大家好我是王刚
Hello everyone this is Wang Gang
本期视频为大家带来一道家常菜
In this video, I'll introduce a homestyle dish
肉末蒸蛋
Steamed eggs with ground meat
首先我们在碗中打入
First, we crack three eggs
鸡蛋三个
in a bowl
加入适量的盐和猪油
add Moderate amount of salt and lard
用筷子将鸡蛋搅散
Use chopsticks to scramble the eggs.
再加入250毫升的温水拌匀
and add 250ml of warm water and mix it together.
然后将蛋液中的泡沫过滤
Then filter out the foam from the eggs
将鸡蛋放入蒸锅中
Place the bowl of eggs in a steamer
碗口盖上一个碟子
cover the bowl with a plate
上汽之后盖上锅盖
Cover the steamer once steaming begins.
开中小火蒸十分钟
On low-medium heat, steam for 10 minutes.
然后准备肉末150克
prepare 150g ground pork
加入盐，料酒和水淀粉拌匀
Add with salt, cooking wine, and a cornstarch slurry.
锅中加入少许食用油
Add some cooking oil to the wok.
加入肉末开小火把肉末煸香
Toss in the ground pork, and stir-fry on low-medium heat until fragrant.
下一步开始调味
Next step is to prepare the seasoning.
加入白糖提鲜
add sugar
加入生抽
Add light soy sauce
再加入老抽上色
Add dark (aged) soy sauce for color.
加入小葱白炒香
Add in chopped green onions and stir-fry until fragrant.
最后加入适量的
Finally add a moderate amount of
水淀粉勾芡
cornstarch slurry
10分钟后取出蒸蛋
After 10 minutes of steaming, take the eggs out.
将肉末铺在蒸蛋上面
Pour the ground pork mixture over the steamed eggs.
即可上菜
ready to serve
一道美味的肉末蒸蛋就制作完成
Now, a very delicious dish of steamed egg with ground meat is done!

